item.title: Error
item.dc:creator: @frank frank_
item.description:
@frank wrote:

because the packet parsing in the RS2 servers is really badly coded it all ends up in one method, which after a while will tend to increase in size rapidly.

if you just “split” the method and then call the new method from that existing one, it should work correctly.
